      "text": "それで、父が大好きだったバイクに乗りたくても\n事故を目の前で見ていたトラウマで乗れなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So even though she wants to ride the motorcycle her father loved so much…\nbut she can’t ride it because of the trauma of seeing the accident…",
